```plantuml
@startuml codahale_sneaker
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor User

rectangle "CLI" as CLI {
}

rectangle "Manager" as Manager #lightblue {
  rectangle "ObjectStorage\nInterface" as ObjectStorage #lightgoldenrodyellow
  rectangle "KeyManagement\nInterface" as KeyManagement #lightgoldenrodyellow
  rectangle "Envelope" as Envelope #lightyellow
}

rectangle "AWS S3" as S3 #mistyrose
rectangle "AWS KMS" as KMS #mistyrose

' ========== Connections ==========
User --> CLI : invoke sneaker commands

CLI --> Manager : parse command and execute

' Manager interactions with S3 and KMS
Manager --> ObjectStorage
Manager --> KeyManagement
Manager --> Envelope

' ObjectStorage interactions
ObjectStorage --> S3 : upload/download/list/delete secrets

' KeyManagement interactions
KeyManagement --> KMS : generate data key\nencrypt/decrypt data key

' Envelope interactions
Envelope --> KeyManagement : request data key
Envelope --> ObjectStorage : encrypt/decrypt secrets with data key

@enduml
```